                                         ProjectFilesystem projectFilesystem,
                                         com.google.common.collect.ImmutableSet<Path> filesToParse,
                                         JavaPackageFinder fallbackPackageFinder)
        Creates a hybrid JavaPackageFinder which will resolve packages for the selected paths based on parsing the source files and use the fallbackPackageFinder for everything else.
        Parameters:
        javaFileParser - parser to read Java sources with.
        projectFilesystem - filesystem.
        filesToParse - set of files to parse.
        fallbackPackageFinder - package finder to use when the package can't be inferred from source.
        Returns:
        the described PackageFinder.
